@baseURL = http://localhost:6969
@urlPath = api/v1
@analyticsPath = analytics

# ─── Prerequisites ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Analytics are computed async via BullMQ workers.  Before running these
# requests you must have already:
#   1. Created a goal        (goals.http)
#   2. Created a task        (tasks.http)
#   3. Completed a session   (sessions.http — WebSocket stopSession or manual)
#   4. Completed a task      (tasks.http — PATCH /:id  { "status": "COMPLETED" })
#
# After each of those actions the workers will run within a few seconds.
# You may hit the endpoints immediately; if data is not yet computed they will
# return 404 (no analytics yet) — just retry.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@goalId = PASTE_GOAL_ID_HERE
@today  = 2026-03-01
@weekStart = 2026-02-23

# ─── Dashboard (composite) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Returns today + this week + all goals + estimation profile in a single call.
# Any section not yet computed is returned as null / [].

### GET dashboard
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Daily analytics ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Computed after every session.complete / task.complete event.
# data.timeLeaks[] — detected focus gaps > 30 min on that day.

### GET daily — today
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/daily?date={{today}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET daily — specific past date
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/daily?date=2026-02-27
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET daily range (heatmap / trend chart)
# Returns an array of daily docs for each day that had activity in the range.
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/daily/range?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate={{today}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Weekly analytics ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Computed every Sunday at 23:00 UTC by the cron fan-out (COMPUTE_WEEKLY_ALL).
# weekStart must be the Monday of the desired week.

### GET weekly — a specific week (give the Monday date)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/weekly?weekStart={{weekStart}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET recent weeks (default 8 — ~2 months, newest first)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/weekly/recent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET recent weeks — custom limit
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/weekly/recent?limit=4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Goal analytics ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Computed when a session or task for that goal is completed.
# Includes: totalLoggedMinutes, completionPercent, consistencyScore (% of
#           last 12 ISO weeks with ≥1 session), projectedCompletionDate, isOnTrack.

### GET analytics for all goals
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### GET analytics for a specific goal
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/goals/{{goalId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Estimation profile ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Updated when a task is marked COMPLETED (if it had an estimatedDuration).
# rollingAverage > 100 → finishing faster than estimated
# rollingAverage < 100 → consistently over-running
# trend: IMPROVING | DECLINING | STABLE  (compares latest 15 vs oldest 15)

### GET estimation accuracy profile
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/estimation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ─── Error cases ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### ❌ GET daily — missing date param (should return 400)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/daily
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ❌ GET daily — bad date format (should return 400)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/daily?date=01-03-2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ❌ GET daily — date with no activity (should return 404)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/daily?date=2000-01-01
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ❌ GET goal analytics — non-existent goal (should return 404)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/goals/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ❌ GET estimation — no tasks completed yet (should return 404)
# Only fires 404 when the profile has never been written for this user.
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/estimation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ❌ GET any analytics endpoint without token (should return 401)
GET {{baseURL}}/{{urlPath}}/{{analyticsPath}}/dashboard

###
